# ============================================================================
# NOTES ON IGNORED DIRECTORIES
# ============================================================================
# input/  → Folder is tracked, contents are not ignored by default
#           (safe - input files should be re-added by team)
# output/ → Folder is tracked, contents are not ignored by default
#           (safe - output files are regenerated by pipeline)
#
# If output becomes too large, selectively ignore:
# output/*.json
# output/*.png
# output/*.jpg
# (But only if truly necessary)

